/******************************
Firebase Configuration for Phone Auth
Production: use Firebase Auth on the client to send SMS OTPs. Configure the Firebase
Admin SDK on the server using either `FIREBASE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_JSON` (JSON string)
or `FIREBASE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_PATH` (path to service account JSON file).
Set `FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID` to help clients if needed.
******************************/


# Example (do NOT commit real credentials):
# FIREBASE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_JSON={"type":"service_account","project_id":"...",...}
# or set a path to a JSON file on the server:
# FIREBASE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_PATH=./secrets/firebase-service-account.json
